#

Spicy Thai Basil Chicken

25 min
$12
320 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

SoyShellfish

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy-FreeHigh-Protein

Cuisine:

Thai

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

QuickStir-frySpicy

Description

A quick and flavorful stir-fry featuring tender chicken, aromatic basil, and a hint of spice.

Ingredients

  • chicken breast, thinly sliced: 1 lb
  • fresh thai basil leaves: 1 cup
  • garlic, minced: 3 cloves
  • soy sauce: 2 tablespoons
  • oyster sauce: 1 tablespoon
  • chili paste or sauce: 1 tablespoon
  • vegetable oil: 2 tablespoons
  • bell pepper, sliced: 1
  • onion, sliced: 1
  • cooked jasmine rice: for serving
